候風正影響廣東。本港方面，<span style=\"color: red;\">今早天文台錄得最低氣溫18.1度，是入秋以來的最低紀錄。</span><br />\n<br />\n在上午八時，熱帶低氣壓天兔集結在胡志明市以東約660公里，預料向西南偏西移動，時速約20公里，橫過南海南部。 同時，颱風萬宜集結在硫黃島之西南偏南約1290公里，預料向西北移動，時速約25公里，橫過西北太平洋。<br />\n<br />\n本港地區今日天氣預測<br />\n<br />\n大致天晴，日間天氣乾燥，最高氣溫約23度。吹和緩至清勁北至東北風。<br />\n<br />\n展望：<br />\n<br />\n明日大致天晴。下週初漸轉多雲有雨。"},{"pid":"a425f4c6ee3c5e1669f429f5e243b05853a00d68","tid":912620,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T01:11:44.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"383651411dff62c3628a71246a7abb2020107964","tid":912620,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"25a2c3d6f7e12c00acb4c9b88039e10d85e858b8","tid":912620,"uid":49918,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T00:41:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T01:12:10.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"8e1c82e97c0478b7269dd8cee3001c937f19e0ec","tid":912620,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"383651411dff62c3628a71246a7abb2020107964","tid":912620,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"25a2c3d6f7e12c00acb4c9b88039e10d85e858b8","tid":912620,"uid":49918,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T00:41:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T01:12:10.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T01:13:09.000Z","msg":"屌得好!"},{"pid":"f48338af7fdfcd35c7f4da3eb9d86fae950c9172","tid":912620,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ff57e97b9484653540ba76a024bc6f1f32246e1","tid":912620,"uid":886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e49b91369f04bd7184bc3d3ed3941342de8427e8","tid":912620,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4dcf3a28260cdcd9f5bb50c57d04acb38d298915","tid":912620,"uid":886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T00:03:15.000Z","msg":"無限熱水暖氣供應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n帶部iPad 杯麵坐成日<img src=\"/assets/fac